data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this home that features TWO master suites, 3 car garage. This home has over 2,200 sq/ft of living space, 4 total bedrooms, 3 total bathrooms and a large kitchen that is open to the dining and living room. We are all hoping for cooler weather, so be prepared with the wood burning fire place in the living room for later this fall and winter. Solar Panels have provided enough energy that the current owner has not had to pay for electric usage all summer! Located conveniently to Fort Cavazos and numerous shopping and restaurants, this home is ready for new owners. BRING ALL OFFERS!
